      "pattern_id": "SUBGRAPH/GeluPattern",
      "pattern_type": "subgraph",
      "pattern_name": "Gelu_Erf_Based",
      "description": "GELU activation function implemented using Erf (Gaussian Error Function). This pattern consists of Div, Erf, Add, and Mul operations that together compute the GELU activation: x * 0.5 * (1 + erf(x / sqrt(2)))",
      "semantic_label": "GELUActivation"
    }
  ],
